						<summary>

						<p>On the left pilaster of the <hi rend="italic">raṅgamaṇḍapa</hi> of the Mahishāsuramardini temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Piṅgaḷa, Chaitra, śu. 15, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Records the improvements made to the temple and also renovation of the ruined <hi rend="italic">dhvajastaṁbha,</hi> by Rājā Mallikārjunaprasāda-Nāyaḍu Bahadaru, son of Rājā Yērlagaḍḍa Aṅkinēḍu Bahadaru. In characters of 17th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
